title: Ep 2644 - Well Kept Surprise
shortDesc: Jethalal is getting phone calls to know what he has planned. But Jethalal refuses to give in. Jethalal's friend from Surat has come to deliver the kites Jethalal ordered. Stay Tuned!

title: Ep 2645 - The Surprise Trip
shortDesc: Jethalal introduces all the types of Kites to the society members and also informs them about a surprise trip for Sankranti.

title: Ep 2646 - Get Ready for the Surprise
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members are all set to embark on their surprise trip. While everyone is waiting, Jethalal is still not ready. The bus arrives and all the society members board the bus to their surprise destination.

title: Ep 2647 - The Kite Festival
shortDesc: Jethalal's surprise has shocked everyone as he has brougt them to the kite festival and also the tallest statue in the world, i.e. Statue of Unity. Everyone is very happy and excited to enjoy the kite festival. Stay Tuned!

title: Ep 2648 - Celebrating Unity
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members have arrived at the Statue of Unity to celebrate Makar Sankranti by participating in the International Kite Festival 2019.

title: Ep 2649 - Statue of Unity
shortDesc: All the Gokhuldhaam members visit the Statue of Unity and have a look around. Everyone shares knowledge about the statue and what it stands for. This episode is dedicated to the 'Iron Man of India', Shri Sardar Vallabh Bhai Patel. Stay Tuned!

title: Ep 2650 - Champaklal Is Missing
shortDesc: A worried Jethalal calls everyone and informs them about the situation and Bhide, Popatlal and Jethalal are out to search Champaklal. Will they find him in time?

title: Ep 2651 - Popatlals Misery
shortDesc: Popatlal does not look very happy, as he tells everyone about how he has to do all his work on his own and that he wants to get married. Will his problems come to an end? Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2652 - A Surprise Visit
shortDesc: Sapna and her aunt Gauri pay a visit to Gokuldham society with an intention of meeting Popatlal. The society members are overjoyed learning that a girl has arrived to meet Popatlal.

title: Ep 2653 - Marriage Proposal for Popatlal
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members welcome Gauri and Sapna presuming that Sapna is interested in marrying Popatlal. But, to their dismay, the one who is interested to marry Popatlal is Gauri, who is much older than Popatlal. What will Popatlal do now?

title: Ep 2654 - The Prank
shortDesc: Popatlal doesn’t know where to run and avoid the marriage proposal from Gauri. Then, Gauri and Sapna inform Popatlal that they have played a prank on him. Popatlal is relieved and has learned a lesson thanks to this prank.

title: Ep 2655 - Tapu Sena Breaking Apart
shortDesc: A guy named Montu has suddenly turned up in Gogi's life and Gogi roams around with him only. Tapu sena notices the change in Gogi's behaviour and try to warn Gogi that Montu is not a good guy and he shouldn't hangout with them. What will happen now?

title: Ep 2656 - Gogi and SuperX
shortDesc: Gogi confronts Tapu Sena and has an argument regarding his friendship with Montu. Where Tapu sena tries to explain that Montu is not a good guy, Gogi does not take it very sportingly. Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2657 - Gogis Demand
shortDesc: Gogi is trying relentlessly to convince his father to gift him the SuperX-100 phone. Roshan Sodhi shares his dilemma with his friends. Bhide asks him not to buy such an expensive phone for Gogi.

title: Ep 2658 - Gogi Lies
shortDesc: Inspite of all the attempts of getting the new phone, when his parents deny his efforts, Montu teaches him to lie to his parents and get the money from them and get the phone. Gogi goes home and lies to his mother regarding the money.
